Notes on bundled data:

The frequency lists in {es,ja,zh,ko}/words/*.txt are derived from the
OpenSubtitles 2018 corpus via HermitDave/FrequencyWords
(https://github.com/hermitdave/FrequencyWords). Redistribution of these lists
follows the spirit of OpenSubtitles' academic/research use terms.

The downloadable .apkg flashcard decks (hosted at storage.googleapis.com)
contain English glosses sourced from CC-CEDICT (CC-BY-SA 4.0), jamdict/JMdict
(CC-BY-SA), Wiktionary (CC-BY-SA), and Google Gemini. Per CC-BY-SA, any
redistribution of glosses must preserve attribution to the originating
dictionaries and license downstream derivatives under a compatible license.
